{"tid":2095293,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【【【初選論壇醜態收集箱】】】重開","createTime":"2020-07-05T10:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T10:24:50.000Z","uid":88743,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"703d95ef3edccfaa966d12d58dca0a6907079542","tid":2095293,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:35:33.000Z","msg":"屌上個PO唔知點解推極都推唔撚郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先拋磚引玉啦<br />\n頭先睇到有PO討論呢位政治家<br />\n忍唔住整左個GIF<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主持問：你點睇新一代抗爭者 以攬炒為前提進入議會呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DrL0VYi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrL0VYi.gif&h=068d8f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">片:</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/e00bwo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fe00bwo&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj36nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=d1591dce\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/e00bwo</a><br />\n<br />\n因為本人仲未得閒睇哂咁多場初選<br />\n呢個post目的係想收集初選各大政治家偉論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲下會再開個ＰＯ或用ｐｉｎ做個整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇左少少初選<br />\n根本無人講國安法 <br />\n個個都係度奶35+奶議席<br />\n言論驚俾人ＤＱ驚撚過閪咁<br />\n睇到反胃<br />\n<br />\n=============================<br />\nＦＹＩ：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200622/4QFCMT7ADVG6PKAMIJ4XGDM4PI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200622%2F4QFCMT7ADVG6PKAMIJ4XGDM4PI%2F&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj36nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=f50e108d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200622%2F4QFCMT7ADVG6PKAMIJ4XGDM4PI%2F&h=09194799\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200622/4QFCMT7ADVG6PKAMIJ4XGDM4PI/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YKKH471.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYKKH471.png&h=b46f91fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡單講又要參選 又要係國安法下縮<br />\n俾你入到議會話知你50+ <br />\n根本係永續社運 係維穩 係打工 係食人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係你就堂堂正正支持國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n縮就同中間派希望聯盟 同袁彌昌無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舊PO<br />\n【初選論壇醜態收集箱】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2094661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2094661</a>"},{"pid":"1669f1396fad317e3912829c9d846952e05cf53c","tid":2095293,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:39:24.000Z","msg":"幫手推下丫屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7ce3ece991d93c11988dfe867a0306c429d491","tid":2095293,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134b1343051469ce558b703d4b01c06caca05bd5","tid":2095293,"uid":313426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:50:35.000Z","msg":"p 牌幫唔到"},{"pid":"71e58ca81d992ea33d686e64046235f4ac01d401","tid":2095293,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:57:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85c03ce5e446ad0fa4ceb0df1a8c4a7ca344bf17","tid":2095293,"uid":138509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T13:20:22.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2166d9e2d7e5bd5100fc36a3feacdcbe26f9decc","tid":2095293,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T13:20:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9fda175dcb0d9a3be6c0ef780885a814e7c98af","tid":2095293,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face