514a327fab9b36dd41d46331e20620a4440","tid":2095293,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T16:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06256a3a35263b00d321ac7aa5222e523b3a5a1","tid":2095293,"uid":202296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T17:17:08.000Z","msg":"九西應該要cap黃碧雲話一齊衝嗰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04c9b23d3571f3badf4a4805279e96b5e56e0d3","tid":2095293,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:24:50.000Z","msg":"琴日又有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n涂謹申<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qCjmKYz2eU4?t=4027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqCjmKYz2eU4%3Ft%3D4027&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj36nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=4684e42c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qCjmKYz2eU4?t=4027</a><br />\n<br />\n1:07:07<br />\n<br />\n王百羽：民主黨黨綱第三條：「我們關心中國，作為中国人民的一分子，香港人有權利及責任去參與及評議國家事務。」如果民主黨孭住「身為中国人」呢個包袱，<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">喺將來中国話唔可以幫助手足嗰陣，喺中国同香港之間，你會揀關心中国定幫助手足</span></span></strong>？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">涂謹申：</span></span></strong>我唔認為呢個係包袱，作為中國人我地應該係可以評議中共點樣國和做得唔好。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個唔係包袱，呢個係中國人既權利！你話我大中華膠都好！我係中国人！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n王百羽：２０２０年啦，我地見到好多大中華膠既前輩都已經作出心態既改變，但涂謹申仍然未能放棄呢個包袱。"}]}